Ungenza impesheni yakho ingabi nentela ekhuza phezulu ngokuhlanganisa intela okumele uyikhokhe. Ungakwazi ukuhlela ngendlela ugcine ungayikhokhile intela. Isamba sikaR500 000 esingakhokhelwa intela Ungakwazi ukukhipha imali elinganiselwa kuR500 000 esikhwameni sakho sempesheni ngaphandle kokukhokha intela. Uma uhlela ukukhipha isamba semali esingaphezulu kukaR500 000 ongayikhokheli intela, kungakusiza kakhulu ukukhuluma nomhleli wengcebo oqeqeshiwe. Abahleli bethu bengcebo bangakukhombisa ukuthi ungakwazi ukukhipha imali engakanani, baphinde bakubonise ngokuthi ukukhipha imali, kungaba nomthelela ongakanani enteleni oyikhokhayo eholweni lakho. Intela ekhokhwa uma uthatha umhlalaphansi Imali oyikhokhela intela esambeni semali  - inani lentela R0 - R500 000              0% wemali oyikhokhela intela R500 001 - R700 000             18% wentela engaphezulu kukaR500 000 R700 001 - R1 050 000              R36 000 + 27% wentela engaphezulu kukaR700 000 R1 050 001 nangaphezulu  Uma sisebenzisa lo mzekelo, iSARS ibheka yonke imali eyake yakhishwa phambilini ngaphambi kokuba ibale intela okumele ikhokhwe esambeni ozohlomula ngaso. Lokhu kubalwa kuko: Sonke isamba sempesheni ozoyihlomula okubalwa nomhlomulo uma uficwa ngukufa kusukela ngo- 1 Okthoba 2007 Yonke imali ekhishiwe yomhlomulo kusukela ngo-1 Mashi 2009 Wonke umhlomulo owuthola uma uyeka emsebenzini kusukela ngo-1 Mashi 2011 Isibonelo: UNomusa Dladla uneminyaka engu-60. Uhlela ukuyeka umsebenzi athathe umhlalaphansi. Unemali elinganiselwa kuR1 million esikhwameni sakhe sempesheni. Ufuna ukukhipha wonke * -1/3 wemali azoyihlomula, ube ngukheshi. Uzosebenzisa imali esalayo ukuthenga uhlelo oluzoqinisekisa ukuthi uyahola ngesikhathi esempeshenini, njenge-retirement annuity okanye i-life guaranteed life annuity. Singakwazi ukusebenzisa lolu lwazi ukubala intela ezokhokhwa nguNomusa esikhwameni sakhe. 1: Bala ukuthi uyimalini u-1/3 esikhwameni sakho sempesheni Isibalo: 1/3 x R1 000 000 Isamba semali esingakhishwa sibe ngukheshi: R333 333 2: Isamba somhlomulo ongakhishwa ube ngukheshi Awuyikhokhi intela esambeni semali elinganiselwa kuR500 000 emhlomulweni wakho wempesheni. Lokhu kusho ukuthi uNomusa ngeke ayikhokhe intela emhlomulweni wakhe onguR333 333 ngenxa yokuthi imali yakhe ingaphansi kukaR500 000. Kubalulekile ukwazi ukuthi lesi sibalo uthatha ngokuthi, ngokokuqala uNomusa ekhipha isamba semali esikhwameni sempesheni. Ukungakhokhi intela kuR500 000 wokuqala, kwenzeka kanye kanti lo mthetho usetshenziswa kuzona zonke izikhwama zakho zempesheni. Bonana nomeluleki wezezimali oqeqeshiwe Akuyona into ongayithatha kancane ukuhlelela umhlalaphansi ngoba ukulondolozela impesheni kungaba yingcebo yakho enkulu. Ngakho kumele wazi ukuthi izinqumo ozithatha manje zingaba nomthelela onjani ekusaseni 
lakho. Ukuhlela nokuzibophezela ekulondolozeni imali yokuya empeshenini kungakwenza ukwazi  ukuthatha umhlalaphansi ngokunethezeka.